  <history>Layer was downloaded as a shapefile by ITOS from HDX. It was then analyzed by ITOS for errors. Those errors were corrected and then the layer was sent back to UNOCHA as a feature class within a file geodatabase. The following was found and fixed by ITOS: 1. 10 Admin2 names were converted to proper case: Pha oudom, Xieng ngeun, Park ou, Pak xeng, Boon neua, Nhot ou, Lao ngarm, Ta oi, KaysonePhomvihane, Keo oudom</history>
